Author: ButterIstLiebe
Text: I guess I could go to a different doctor. But I don't really have the energy and at the moment I feel way too healthy to try it again? Maybe when I lose some more weight because I don't wanted the humiliation of not being taken seriously again

Author: fallaciousfeline
Text: Are you able to change doctors (again)? You need someone to take you and your concerns seriously
